Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.82,0:01:35.45,Title 3,ep,0,0,0,,{\fad(776,642)\pos(197,810)\fscx(86)}Episode 15: Justice Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.99,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,Polnareff... I want you dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:40.70,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,I'm going to avenge my son by ripping out your innards!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:45.12,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,But right now, I can't let him find Hol Horse's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:43.04,Secondary,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Hey, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.67,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,She's not behind the counter, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:51.09,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,Things will only get worse if the other three show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.80,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,I need to kill them one by one, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.38,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,Just stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.55,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Ma'am, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.76,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I think I just heard something crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.35,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:11.15,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Ma'am, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.48,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.95,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,What happened, ma'am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.70,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Don't mind me, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:23.99,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I simply fell and banged my hip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.20,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,You fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:28.21,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,That's really dangerous, especially after burning your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.25,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,You sure are absent-minded. {Brolicious: absentminded without hyphen is probably okay too, but OED has it with... and I am a dictionary hipster}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.92,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.09,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Please excuse me... I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.09,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Your concern is appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:37.42,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,Get the hell out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:40.01,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,Who the hell let you in here, goddammit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.65,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,I'll spare you my wrath for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:57.15,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,But soon, I'll kill you just like I did Hol Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.15,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,All it takes is a tiny wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:03.91,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,...and I can turn you into a puppet for my Justice to control!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.96,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Here we go... your staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.50,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You're dripping with sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:16.00,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,N-No, really, pay me no mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.01,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Please just rest in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.22,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:24.39,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,But aren't you running this hotel all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.68,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Don't you have any family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.64,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Maybe a son?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.52,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:38.15,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,N-Nothing, I was just going to say I've grown fond of living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.15,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Oh? I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.32,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,But aren't you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.41,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Like, say your son had a wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:50.37,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Your grandkids would be happily running around the lobby right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.91,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,They might be noisy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:54.00,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,...aren't families great?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.84,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,If you had kids, you think they'd be older than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.13,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.55,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Did they move to the big city or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.64,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,N-No... They've passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:12.73,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Oh, I-I'm so sorry. I've been so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:17.36,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,You're the cretin that killed him, goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.82,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,I'm going to murder you! Murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.53,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Here, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.41,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Want a shoulder rub?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.20,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I'm all alone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.08,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I lost my mother when I was really young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.08,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,All of this makes me remember her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.29,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Just for tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.42,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,...you can call me your son...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.76,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,...and ask me whatever! {His face kills me XD}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.34,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,You stinking brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.76,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,Maybe I really should just kill you right now!{Xemnas: Bit more accurate.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.31,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Whoa, you're really tense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.68,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I guess you've had it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.99,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Wh-Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.99,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,H-Hol Horse? You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:12.50,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,He must have made his Stand disappear \Nbefore he shot himself in the mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.25,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Th-That face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.00,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,P-Polnareff! Behind ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.76,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,It's Hol Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.26,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:24.92,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:29.80,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Silence! I know you're the one who\N murdered J. Geil, because I'm his mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.69,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Chariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.69,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,You're a Stand user?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.94,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Those responsible for murdering my son shall die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.61,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:47.82,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:51.37,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I've already ensured you can't contact the other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.54,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:59.54,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I've summoned some friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.96,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.46,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I-It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:10.51,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,That Indian traveler we found dead when we first got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.06,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,How are they moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:28.74,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,This is my Stand Justice's ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:35.66,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,A person can have no more than one Stand, \Nbut my Justice bypasses this by controlling corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:41.54,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,It can control hundreds, even thousands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.92,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Aren't you taking this needless grudge a bit far?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:49.93,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,To think that such a twisted Stand user was after us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:53.18,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,This here town... wants y'all dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.68,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,And if ya get so much as a scratch, this'll happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:07:00.77,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,All I need is one tiny wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.27,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Just a little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:06.61,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Then my Stand, Justice, will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.36,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.36,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.95,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,Polnareff! Ya can't just leave me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:19.16,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Fuck off! Did you already forget about Abdul?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.83,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I have no reason to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.38,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,You can die for all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.80,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,You can't escape, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.67,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I'll rip your brain out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.30,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I'll snap your spine in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.34,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I'll crush your balls! {Xemnas: CR and their censorship}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.85,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I shall avenge my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.31,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,How terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.52,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,How can an old woman run this fast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.06,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:50.19,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Shit! He ran into the back room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.78,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,After him! Break down the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.08,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,W-What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.79,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,This hallway leads down into the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:07.04,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Even if I tried to yell for Mr. Joestar and the others, \NI'm too far away for them to hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:12.88,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I think I'd be fine fighting on my own, \Nbut I'll be in big trouble if I get so much as a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.30,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,She'll do anything to take control of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.26,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,D-Damn... Isn't there a way outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.73,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I can't get out the window with those bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.77,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.74,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I'll hide in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.28,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,The door just broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.49,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I might end up having to fight them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:41.62,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,But I can't let them land even a single scratch on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.46,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I can hear them in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.17,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,They must be checking the other doors...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.67,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Crap, they're getting closer by the second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.92,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,And what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.84,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Am I in a bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:59.39,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Why am I always getting attacked in the bathroom...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.14,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Shit, the toilet is so dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:05.19,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,All right, come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:10.52,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,But the second you walk in,\N my Chariot will chop you all up in a single breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.62,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.08,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Now I can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.42,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Those things... and that hag...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.67,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,What the hell are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:37.26,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Aren't they going to break down the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.39,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,What are they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.52,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Just do something already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.91,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,They saw me from the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.41,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,The fuck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.54,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Sh-Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.38,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,He stabbed my tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:21.55,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Well done! \NHe's finally fallen under my Justice's control!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.76,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,You fucking little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:34.32,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I'm going to crush your stupid face \Nif you don't open that door right this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.07,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Now laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.04,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,How pitiful, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.67,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Very pitiful, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:11:04.31,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Because of your act of cowardice, my son, J. Geil, \Ndied feeling even more pitiful and upset than you do this very moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:11.27,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Now then... Why don't we have you \Nmake this bathroom spotless, Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:23.99,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Lick the toilet until it shines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.20,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Lick it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:31.79,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Lick... it... all... up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.75,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.88,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,A-Anything but that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.39,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.99,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:12.46,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,W-What is it? There's no reason to barge in without knocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.08,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.96,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'm looking for Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.51,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,And I did knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:22.72,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Maybe you didn't hear me since you were doing something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.72,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:38.48,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'm looking for Polnareff. You seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.74,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:49.37,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,Jotaro is clever, unlike Polnareff, \Nand will know the right questions to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:53.62,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,He'll think I'm suspicious if I play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.13,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:03.88,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,I'll tell him the truth, and as soon as he\N turns his back to me, I'll stab him with my scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.64,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,After that, my Stand will kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.72,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:15.85,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I know exactly where Mr. Polnareff is, Mr. Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:27.70,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Crap... Jotaro doesn't know even \Nthe smallest scratch will defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.74,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,S-Stay away! Go tell Mr. Joestar and Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.29,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,That old hag is the Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:37.54,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,He was just here. Right now he's using the toilet, Mr. Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:46.05,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Really, the toilet? Behind this door?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.72,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:54.77,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Just go through that door, \Nand it's the last door at the end of the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:58.77,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,You fool! You really are just a stupid brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.82,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,Killing Polnareff will make my son in heaven happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:07.24,Thoughts,Enya,0,0,0,,If I kill Jotaro, Lord Dio in Egypt will be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.03,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:12.24,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I forgot to ask, old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:20.21,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Oh my, what's the matter, old lady? Looks like you fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.25,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Did you trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.21,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,T-Too close...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.26,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Oh, that could have been really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.13,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Running while holding scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.22,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,What a relief nothing bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.56,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Such a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:39.02,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Sorry to ask while you're down, but I have another question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.73,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Why did you just call me Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:48.24,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I didn't tell you my name, and nobody said it in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.49,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.95,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Come on, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:59.92,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because I liked {\i1}Columbo{\i0} as a kid, \Nbut when something bothers me, I become restless. {Apparently the main theme of Columbo was that the audience knew who the perp was before Lt. Columbo did, and thus the format of the show was watching him make them squirm as he exposes them. Definitely a fitting reference here. Brolicious: In particular, Columbo was famous for saying "oh that's right, there was one more thing" or similar, so the ref is spot on}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:03.38,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,W-Why do you suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.63,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,The hotel register!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:10.01,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,You wrote your name on the hotel register earlier, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.47,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,It's so dry in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.18,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,You wrote "Kujo Jotaro."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.47,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:20.23,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,When you say "hotel register," you mean this? {TLC on this. It sounds like too much dialogue for "You mean this thing?"}{Xemnas: There we go.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:24.65,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly that! {Lol, for the last two frames of this line, there's a red exclamation point. It's like subliminally telling the watcher that SOMETHING HAPPENED!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.99,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Kujo Qtaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.70,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,"Jotaro" isn't written anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:36.87,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I suspected you from the moment \Nyou said "Joestar" when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.37,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I told the others not to use my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.17,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,And yet, somehow you knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.26,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,So quit playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:52.63,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I already know you're one of the Stand users that's after us, hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.10,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Well, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.02,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna show me your Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:06.57,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I've already shown you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:10.24,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora! Ora! Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:14.91,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.66,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.43,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,My Stand, Justice, has triumphed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:38.56,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I just need one spot! One little spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.85,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,You've fallen into my trap, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.85,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:48.52,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,Jotaro, it's me, Hol Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.69,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,Enya's got herself a fog Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.95,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,Yer wound'll turn into a hole like mine, then she'll control ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.95,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,She can even control corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.70,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth, Hol Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.41,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:08.71,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.09,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Can you punch fog with your fist?
