Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.68,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Useless! Absolutely useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:22.43,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,You pests can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.69,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,She's got the strongest Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:29.02,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,Them puny Stands of ours're useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.44,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,Nothing'll beat that Stand! {Stand Stand Stand Stand}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:34.28,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, keep it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:37.53,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Keep pouring on the compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:42.58,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Now, Jotaro, I'll control you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:47.08,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,R-Run, Jotaro! She'll put a hole in your leg! {I was confused by this line at first since it a zombie minion already looked like it made a hole in Jotaro's leg earlier, but Enya makes a hole out of the wound so this line still makes sense.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.38,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.42,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,No need to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:56.55,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Before this fucking hag takes another breath,\N my Stand will defeat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.72,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Oh? What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:03.72,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Before I do what one more time? \NYou stupid little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.27,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Before I take another breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.85,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I'll do that right—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.57,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,Just one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.16,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:29.12,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Jotaro's Star Platinum is inhaling Justice's face! {I just want to go on record and say that this is the DUMBEST THING EVER. In the entire manga, from 1987 to 2014, this is definitely the most retarded way that a fight ends.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:33.63,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,P-Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:36.09,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,And he's holding it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.30,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Soon she won't be able to breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:55.65,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:59.20,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Looks like her head is full...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.28,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...of the fog she liked to play around with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.20,Main,Enya,0,0,0,,I'm so mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:13.59,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Why the hell do you even care what I've been licking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.25,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Quit asking stupid questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.84,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Cough, cough, the toilet, cough...
