Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.84,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I didn't quite catch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.76,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Who even cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:27.27,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I want to disinfect my tongue! \NJust get me some medicine!
