Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:37.48,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,But I can't resist messing with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:41.78,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Hey! Did Jotaro already tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.62,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,You fucking old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.12,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,He's messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.58,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Forget about the medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.41,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,All right, all right. My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.96,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'll fix you right up, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.17,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It'll get infected if we don't take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.46,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:58.92,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Toilet licker...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.43,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Goddammit! Let's get back to our journey! Jotaro! Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.26,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Everyone, get outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.56,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,What on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:18.57,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,One step outside, and now this place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.95,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,It's a graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:26.74,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,She was using her Stand's fog to make this graveyard look like a town with a hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:32.37,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,So we were talking to the corpses that were buried in these graves...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:45.01,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,T-Take her with us? The old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.55,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:54.27,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,We need to know how many more Stand users there are, \Nwhat their powers are, and where in Egypt Dio is hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.81,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Not to mention what Dio's Stand's power is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:21:01.28,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,If we can get the old lady to tell us that alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:04.28,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...we'll have a major advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:08.99,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I highly doubt she'll tell us, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:14.29,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,We just need to use my Hermit Purple \Nto project what she's thinking onto a TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:19.46,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Now I see! \NSince there's no TV here, we'll just do it in the next town!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:23.01,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Hol Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.26,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.55,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Our car!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:28.68,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,I'll be payin' Dio a vist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.80,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:32.81,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,So long as ya ain't killed first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.27,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,But lemme warn ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.85,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,Kill the old lady soon as ya can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:44.07,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,She'll show ya just how scary Dio really is if ya don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:45.82,Main,Hol Horse,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:50.83,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,What the hell is he talking about?
