Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:33.18,Secondary,Steely Dan,0,0,0,,Lord Dio truly trusts no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.18,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,They should have no problem shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:34.43,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,When I say I'll do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:38.48,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,They both flew back at the same time!
